headline: 2 High-Quality Dividend Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: Despite multiple optimistic forecasts for the S&P 500 heading into 2025, the benchmark index is down 3.6% year to date as of this writing.  In good times and bad, dividend stocks can serve as a stabilizing element for your portfolio.  Here are two high-quality dividend stocks that investors can rely on in volatile markets.
